item.title: CVE-2021-24350|2024-08-03T19:28:23.777Z -- unknown -- visitors
item.description: The Visitors WordPress plugin through 0.3 is affected by an Unauthenticated Stored Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability. The plugin would display the user's user agent string without validation or encoding within the WordPress admin panel.
